cs.IR, cs.DL, cs.CL, cs.CY, cs.CR

This paper is about detecting off-topic mementos within web archive collections, which involves analyzing the content of archived web pages. This topic is closely related to information retrieval (cs.IR), digital libraries (cs.DL), and natural language processing (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper discusses potential issues such as hacking and cybersecurity (cs.CR) and the importance of identifying off-topic content for research purposes (cs.CY).
